name: Mealbasket-in
body:
### Welcome to MealBasket-In.
This repository contains code-base for a simple, intuitive, bootstrap web app that manages online ordering system of a SMB Owner.

### Technology Used
HTML5-CSS3 compatible
NodeJs
KrakenJs
Bootstrap

### Authors and Contributors
